{"tid":488912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屁孩連轟警4槍　中彈警送潤滑液：入獄很需要","createTime":"2017-12-04T07:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T07:56:34.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b57c08b185c13bf19b34a0fdc67d36ded21513a5","tid":488912,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/_data/i/upload/2017/12/03/20171203211346-b0485c98-me.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2F_data%2Fi%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F20171203211346-b0485c98-me.jpg&h=89191f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖／翻攝自《每日郵報》<br />\n美國佛羅里達州一名現年21歲男子羅哈斯（Kevin Rojas），2016年3月還是19歲時，與女友發生爭吵後開車出門，隨後被一名員警攔下，沒想到男子竟朝他連開3槍，其中一槍擊中員警臉部。近日羅哈斯被判處無期徒刑，大難不死的員警在庭上送給他KY潤滑液，因為「入獄後很需要」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/_data/i/upload/2017/12/03/20171203211349-26d3a2df-me.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2F_data%2Fi%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F20171203211349-26d3a2df-me.jpg&h=b2969d16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，羅哈斯在與女友吵架後開車出門，在路上出現魯莽駕駛的情況，被當天休假送14歲兒子上學的員警發現後，試圖將他截停。沒想到羅哈斯下車後，一連朝著員警開了4槍，其中一槍擊中員警的臉部。雖然遭槍擊的員警當下也開槍還擊，但羅哈斯還是成功逃逸，一直到其他員警趕抵支援後，才順利將他逮捕，並以一級謀殺未遂、過失殺人罪、兩項嚴重襲擊執法人員將他起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/_data/i/upload/2017/12/03/20171203211344-79383e51-me.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2F_data%2Fi%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F20171203211344-79383e51-me.jpg&h=892cbfbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n羅哈斯日前遭判處無期徒刑，遭槍擊大難不死的員警現身聆聽法官判決，並在法庭上表示，自己遭槍擊時，見到鮮血四濺，就知道自己被擊中了，並對羅哈斯說，「但當我開始反擊時，你就像個懦夫一樣逃跑」。而該名員警隨後也拿出一包KY潤滑液，向羅哈斯表示「我有份小禮物給你，你要去的地方，你會需要用到很多這個。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/829176\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F829176&d=fvfZ903C9G%2BtEKZ90tb7w%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=8b338f49\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/829176</a>"},{"pid":"b9908047623606564aa6ed37f71f312da3855cd2","tid":488912,"uid":130438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:21:31.000Z","msg":"人地可能本身就0仔"},{"pid":"ecd50299007f89994447e2292b8b70cdb57a2432","tid":488912,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:23:11.000Z","msg":"wow"},{"pid":"8669c221fed9048f2480afcab90d55f2e75501ab","tid":488912,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"強國人比人爆頭都唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a4d1f32b11865efb1ebdf3b69b52b0a679984d","tid":488912,"uid":152726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:56:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強國人比人爆頭都唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能中面無爆頭，any肥，唔死得仲咁幽默"}]}